INSTITUTIONS

Kraken is your trusted and secure crypto partner

LIQUIDITY

Kraken has the liquidity to fuel your business.

OTC

Our OTC desk offers high-touch spot trading at scale, as well as access to bespoke derivatives for risk management and alpha generation to eligible counterparties. 

Spot

Benefit from over 100 assets and hundreds of fiat, crypto and stablecoin trading pairs, and access to leverage with high margin limits, advanced order types and fully featured APIs.

CLIENT SUPPORT

Expert support for professional & institutional traders

Kraken offers 24/7 access to our dedicated Institutional Relationships and Account Management teams via email, phone, or a preferred encrypted messaging service.

Whether you're a family office, broker, high-frequency trader or anything in between, we provide the most attentive service in the industry. Your Kraken representatives are assigned based on your specific needs, so you get the best person to help, every time.

 

SECURITY

Kraken sets the industry

standard for security. 

Security is at the core of Kraken’s DNA, which is why we have a flawless security record after over ten years of business. As a crypto-native organization, Kraken’s long-standing reputation for its emphasis on security has continued to set industry standards through our comprehensive controls, which have been designed to prevent the theft of financial assets or information. 

Our clients consequently entrust us with billions of dollars worth of on-chain assets, including more ETH2 locked up for long-term staking than any other peer exchange.
